  "detailed_description": "<h1>DEMO NOW AVAILABLE</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/7a44d26545096ef231cc27606d8239bc.poster.avif?t=1698115662\" width=620 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/7a44d26545096ef231cc27606d8239bc.webm?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/7a44d26545096ef231cc27606d8239bc.mp4?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/4c1fde0c63b8760b49c511aff9723e20.avif?t=1698115662\" width=650 height=150 /></span><br><i>Glass Wings</i> is a fast paced third-person parkour platformer. Vault, jump, roll, and slide your way through the beautiful minimalist metropolis to hone your skills. Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate freerunner?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/7fb29fa429cb4636faea433ac2b89a51.webp?t=1698115662\" width=620 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRAVERSAL</h2>Utilize a variety of movements to quickly traverse a thrilling environment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/adc75dfd23627f27b6430781c3372a81.poster.avif?t=1698115662\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/adc75dfd23627f27b6430781c3372a81.webm?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/adc75dfd23627f27b6430781c3372a81.mp4?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FLOW</h2>Carefully crafted linear levels ensure you never have to break your parkour flow.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/f0619579aa6d11fccea79e3a77b636e7.poster.avif?t=1698115662\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/f0619579aa6d11fccea79e3a77b636e7.webm?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/f0619579aa6d11fccea79e3a77b636e7.mp4?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STUNNING PLAYGROUNDS</h2>Inspired by classic games of the genre, <i>Glass Wings</i> features a simplified cityscape designed specifically for freerunning.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/2375761a4188c10becfbd01f8d9880d9.poster.avif?t=1698115662\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/2375761a4188c10becfbd01f8d9880d9.webm?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/2375761a4188c10becfbd01f8d9880d9.mp4?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MORE TO COME</h2><i>Glass Wings</i> is a short 20 minute proof of concept parkour experience designed to gather player feedback and funding for <i>Glass Wings 2.0</i>. As a solo developer, your support and feedback is of great value, and essential to improving present systems for the next iteration of <i>Glass Wings</i>. Thank you for playing, and being apart of my journey!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/b1adf974532dfe3817367c02d37b635b.webp?t=1698115662\" width=620 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/4b962d961a5e8d6bd18db342fb6ebff1.poster.avif?t=1698115662\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/4b962d961a5e8d6bd18db342fb6ebff1.webm?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/4b962d961a5e8d6bd18db342fb6ebff1.mp4?t=1698115662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271520/extras/94ed5eae4f2a278685f3a9b8d8f49cf4.webp?t=1698115662\" width=620 height=50 /></span>",
